cast.name: 亚历克斯·琼斯 Alex Jones

this_title: Conspiracy Theory With Jesse Ventura Season 1
introduction: 曾经是WWE职业摔跤手的Jesse Ventura和他的团队一起，调查当代最神秘的阴谋和秘密，如全球变暖、911事件的真相等。He's undertaken some of the most dangerous missions in the world as a Navy SEAL. He's body-slammed giants in the wrestling ring as a WWE superstar. He's even conquered politics as the governor of Minnesota. Now, Jesse Ventura is about to face his greatest challenge yet: uncovering the most compelling, modern-day conspiracy theories. "CONSPIRACY THEORY" is produced by A. Smith & Co. Productions (Hell's Kitchen, I Survived a Japanese Game Show, Kitchen Nightmares).
